		<text id="45" type="text/plain" rect="(1557.1224489795918, 1175.4897959183675, 229.0, 317.80219780219795)" font-family=".AppleSystemUIFont" font-size="16">True Positive:

Actual: Fraud
Predicted: Fraud

= Good!


True Negative: 

Actual: Legitimate
Predicted: Legitmate

= Good!


</text>
		<text id="46" type="text/plain" rect="(1772.8414442700155, 1175.5102040816328, 269.38775510204096, 453.0612244897959)" font-family=".AppleSystemUIFont" font-size="16">False Positive:

Actual: Legitimate
Predicted: Fraud

= Bad!


False Negative:

Actual: Fraud
Predicted: Legitimate

= Very Bad!

</text>
		<text id="47" type="text/plain" rect="(1607.6923076923067, 1592.3076923076924, 125.27472527472537, 50.0)" font-family=".AppleSystemUIFont" font-size="16">Higher % better</text>
